data.description: You won't want to miss this one! This NW beauty stands two stories tall and offers 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms. It showcases a sparkling blue pool with a water feature! But wait, there is more! We can't forget the splashes of fresh paint throughout the interior walls. There is plenty of space for entertaining inside or outside. The backyard offers lush real grass!!
